description:
It's a big hit for the Predator franchise, so how does it fare in Doug's opinion? DisneyCember continues with Predator: Badlands.

Watch all DisneyCember here - https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0AQIMR-tpomecW19RN2LNrdoqd5wFu4R

Watch the new NC - https://youtu.be/EkbsPkmj1hQ

Predator: Badlands is a 2025 American science fiction action film directed by Dan Trachtenberg and written by Patrick Aison from a story by Trachtenberg and Aison. The seventh installment in the Predator franchise, it stars Elle Fanning and Dimitrius Schuster-Koloamatangi in leading roles. It follows Dek, a young exiled Yautja, who crash-lands on a hostile planet and must prove himself worthy of the hunt by killing an apex predator, leading him to form an alliance with Thia, a Weyland-Yutani Corporation android.
